'''咽鼓管唾液腺'''（英语：'''Tubarial salivary gland'''），是一种位于人类的[[鼻腔|鼻腔]]和[[咽喉|咽喉]]之间的器官。该腺体于2020年9月被{{le|荷兰癌症研究所|Netherlands Cancer Institute}}的科学家通过PSMA [[PET-CT|PET/CT]]扫描发现。<ref>{{Cite web|title=New pair of salivary glands in humans discovered|url=https://www.thehindu.com/sci-tech/science/new-pair-of-salivary-glands-in-humans-discovered/article32915485.ece|date=October 22, 2020|last=Pacha|first=Aswathi|via=www.thehindu.com|accessdate=2020-10-24|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209120719/https://www.thehindu.com/sci-tech/science/new-pair-of-salivary-glands-in-humans-discovered/article32915485.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Scientists discover possible new organ in the human throat|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/10/21/health/new-organ-throat-scn-wellness/index.html|last=CNN|first=Katie Hunt and Kristen Rogers|website=CNN|accessdate=2020-10-24|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112224114/https://www.cnn.com/2020/10/21/health/new-organ-throat-scn-wellness/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Scientists Just Discovered a Mysterious Organ Lurking in The Centre of The Human Head|url=https://www.sciencealert.com/chance-discovery-reveals-mysterious-organ-lurking-in-human-head-missed-for-centuries|last=Dockrill|first=Peter|website=ScienceAlert|accessdate=2020-10-24|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122214439/https://www.sciencealert.com/chance-discovery-reveals-mysterious-organ-lurking-in-human-head-missed-for-centuries|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Cancer researchers discover new salivary gland|url=https://medicalxpress.com/news/2020-10-cancer-salivary-gland.html|website=medicalxpress.com|accessdate=2020-10-24|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106072924/https://medicalxpress.com/news/2020-10-cancer-salivary-gland.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=The tubarial salivary glands: A potential new organ at risk for radiotherapy|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0167814020308094|last=Valstar|first=Matthijs H.|last2=de Bakker|first2=Bernadette S.|journal=Radiotherapy and Oncology|doi=10.1016/j.radonc.2020.09.034|year=2020|issn=0167-8140|last3=Steenbakkers|first3=Roel J.H.M.|last4=de Jong|first4=Kees H.|last5=Smit|first5=Laura A.|last6=Klein Nulent|first6=Thomas J.W.|last7=van Es|first7=Robert J.J.|last8=Hofland|first8=Ingrid|last9=de Keizer|first9=Bart|first11=Alfons J.M.|last11=Balm|last10=Jasperse|first10=Bas|access-date=2020-10-24|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212035918/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0167814020308094|dead-url=no}}</ref>

咽鼓管唾液腺平均长约1.5英寸（3.9厘米），在[[咽鼓管|咽鼓管]]隆凸的软骨之上。该唾液腺很可能是人体用来润滑和湿润位于鼻和口腔后面的上咽喉部。<ref>{{Cite web|title=科学家发现人体新器官咽鼓管唾液腺-新华网|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/science/2020-10/23/c_139460736.htm|accessdate=2020-10-24|work=www.xinhuanet.com|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127020439/http://www.xinhuanet.com/science/2020-10/23/c_139460736.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

但此是否为人类第四大唾腺，目前并未受到医学界普遍认同。

== 发现 ==
荷兰癌症研究所的研究人员在对[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]患者进行扫描时注意到了这个尚未被发现的腺体。该研究所的Wouter Vogel博士为证实这一发现，对100个患者进行扫描以及对两具尸体进行解剖。研究小组在''Radiotherapy and Oncology''杂志上公布了此发现。<ref name=":0" />

